title: IHEC, Iraq Elections 2010 : Current PM Maliki Leading, Iraq, March 22, 2010
name: IHEC, Iraq Elections 2010 : Current PM Maliki Leading, Iraq, March 22, 2010
description:
The poly shapefile shows a subset of 7 of Iraq's 18 provinces where Prime Minister Maliki's "State Law" party holds lead.

Look elsewhere on the Finder! for data on provinces where the former PM Allawi's party "Iraqia", Iran-backed party "National Unity" and Kurdish parties in the lead in northern provinces.

author.source: Iraq's Independent High Election Commission Website
